Characters have a set of skills that define areas in which they have specific training. These are rolled in tandem with an [[Aptitude|▽ Aptitude]] when making a [[test|Tests]].

! The Skills
This droplet introduces a set of 14 skills that cover a wide range of training and capabilities. See the individual skill pages linked below for details on each skill and assocaited talents.

* {{Acrobatics}}
* {{Athletics}}
* {{Crime}}
* {{Exploration}}
* {{Investigation}}
* {{Leadership}}
* {{Medicine}}
* {{Performance}}
* {{Persuasion}}
* {{Propriety}}
* {{Scholarship}}
* {{Stealth}}
* {{Survival}}
* {{Taming}}

During play //Skills// are generally paired with an //Aptitude// to determine the total die pool rolled. In general the //Skill// is determined by what you are doing and the //Aptitude// is determined by how you are going about it. In all cases the choice is driven by the narrative.

